org.assertj.swing.data
Interface TableCellFinder

All Known Implementing Classes:
TableCellByColumnId, TableCellInRowByValue, TableCellInSelectedRow
public interface TableCellFinder

Finds a cell in a JTable.

Author:
Alex Ruiz

Method Summary
 TableCell findCell(JTable table, JTableCellReader cellReader)
          Finds a cell in the given JTable based on some search criteria specified by this finder.
 

Method Detail

findCell

@RunsInEDT
@Nonnull
TableCell findCell(@Nonnull
                                     JTable table,
                                     @Nonnull
                                     JTableCellReader cellReader)
Finds a cell in the given JTable based on some search criteria specified by this finder. Implementations of this method should access the given JTable in the event dispatch thread (EDT.)

Parameters:
table - the target JTable.
cellReader - knows how to read the contents of a cell in a JTable.
Returns:
the cell found, if any.
Throws:
ActionFailedException - if a matching cell could not be found.
